{"id": "art-391", "label": "Art. 391", "title": "Art. 391: Soluţionarea cauzei", "slug": "art-391", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1732968183\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1733\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1732968183\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 391: Solu&#355;ionarea\ncauzei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_906212969\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1732\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_906212969\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Deliberarea, redactarea &#351;i pronun&#355;area\nhot&#259;rârii se fac într-un termen de maximum 60 de zile de la închiderea\ndezbaterilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_984367379\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1731\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_984367379\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)La închiderea dezbaterilor, pre&#351;edintele\ncompletului informeaz&#259; p&#259;r&#355;ile &#351;i persoana\nv&#259;t&#259;mat&#259; prezente asupra datei &#351;i modalit&#259;&#355;ii de\npronun&#355;are a hot&#259;rârii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_905770794\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1730\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_905770794\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazuri temeinic justificate, dac&#259; deliberarea,\nredactarea &#351;i pronun&#355;area hot&#259;rârii nu pot avea loc în termenul\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (1), instan&#355;a poate amâna succesiv\npronun&#355;area, fiecare amânare neputând dep&#259;&#351;i 30 de zile. În\ntoate cazurile, deliberarea, redactarea &#351;i pronun&#355;area hot&#259;rârii\nnu pot avea loc mai târziu de 120 de zile de la închiderea dezbaterilor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}